Subject: Re: [T2] Friday topic, ID this bolt? M8x1.0 x 25mm

I know that 9x1x25 Bolts are used on the Bay Bus and Vanagon
differentials/R&Ps

According to the Standard Parts List in ETKA 7, the 8x1x25 Bolt Grade
10.9 is N0101023, but the ATP (Where Used Search) doesn't say what it
goes to.
